deck: Terrance Zdunich is a California based artist currently working on writing and drawing a 12-part comic book series entitled The Molting. deck:
Creator of Los Luchadores Mysteriosos.

Evan Quiring hails from Winnipeg, Manitoba, Canada
description:
Los Luchadores Mysteriosos #1 premiered in April, 2010.   Published through Ronin Studios, this ongoing series not only showcases Evan’s art but also marks his debut as a writer.   Teamed up with colorist (and fellow Winnipegger) Victoria Free, Los Luchadores Mysteriosos is Evan’s way of paying homage to some of his favorite genres, including Lucha Libre (obviously) and B-Movies from the fifties and sixties.
 
From 2002-2003 he drew three stories for the comic book, Mortal Coils (published by Redy Eye Press).  He also drew for 911: Emergency Relief.
name: Evan Quiring
